message: Removed the problem where t0 was ignored. Changed the organisation of the functions and used mroe consistent variable names. Removed the mention of parallel selection which was not implemented. Inlined the function which did not do much.
Corrected ProgressMeter to display loading correctly. Adjusted code to adhere to the 80 character line width limit.
fixed ResidueGroup and SegmentGroup RecordType access
Fixes Issue #1582  AtomGroup.dimensions now always returns a copy

Test case for the t0 argument being ignored. Corrected the original test_SurvivalProbability. The first point has to be 0 (autocorrelation). I changed the universe for the test so that the timeseries is not only 1s (meaning that nothing changes and the test is too naive). This could be further improved by using actual verified values.
